                     <p>Autograph of <persname normal="Gray, Thomas,         1716-1771">Gray</persname>'s four lines, preceding a transcript in 
								<persname normal="Gray, Thomas, 1716-1771">Gray</persname>'s hand 
								of the 12 lines composed by <extref href="http://www.thomasgray.org/resources/glnames.shtml#Mason, William, 1724-1797"
                                show="replace"
                                linktype="simple">
                           <persname normal="Mason, William, 1724-1797">Mason</persname>
                        </extref>, the whole entitled <title render="doublequote" linktype="simple">Epitaph</title>, endorsed in the hand of 
								<extref href="http://www.thomasgray.org/resources/glnames.shtml#Hurd, Richard, 1720-1808"
                                show="replace"
                                linktype="simple">
                           <persname normal="Hurd, Richard, 1720-1808">Richard
										Hurd</persname>
                        </extref> "Mr. Mason's Ep. on his wife in Mr.
								Gray's hand-writing", in the papers of <persname normal="Hurd,           Richard, 1720-1808">Richard Hurd</persname>.
							</p>
